== 风暴 ==

=== 第一号飓风 ===
{{Infobox Hurricane Small
|Basin=Atl
|Image=1925 Atlantic hurricane 1 track.png
|Formed=8月18日
|Dissipated=8月21日
|1-min winds=70
|Pressure=<994
}}
8月17日，有船只在[[海面温度|水温]]超过25.5[[摄氏度|°C]]的热带大西洋海域发现热带天气系统发展，并测得时速65公里大风<ref name="Hur1">{{cite web | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190320/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/excelfiles_centerfix/192501.xls | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | title = Raw Observations for Hurricane One 1925 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/excelfiles_centerfix/192501.xls | format = [[Microsoft_Excel|XLS]] }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]次日凌晨0点，系统成为热带低气压，估计持续风速为每小时45公里。约18小时后，气旋在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东北偏北洋面增强成本季第一场热带风暴。风暴保持逐渐强化的趋势并向东北移动，<ref name="hurdat">{{cite web | title = Atlantic Best Tracks, 1851 to 2007 Reanalyzed | year = 2009 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tra51to07-2125rean.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182612/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tra51to07-2125rean.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref><ref name="RA" />于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月20日早上6点成为飓风<ref name="hurdat" />。约30分钟后，有船只测得每小时75公里风速<ref name="Hur1" />和993.6[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）[[气压|气压]]<ref name="MWR" />，这也是正式记载中风暴的最低气压<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="Hur1" />。不久后，气旋达到风力时速130公里的最高强度，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下已属一级飓风<ref name="hurdat" />。风暴的前进速度加快，转向北上后于8月21日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="hurdat" /><ref name="RA">{{cite web | author = Chris Landsea | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040238/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/presentations/irr-19111930.ppt | deadurl = no | date = 2005-06-28 | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | title = The Atlantic Hurricane Database Reanalysis for 1911 to 1930 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/presentations/irr-19111930.ppt | format = [[Microsoft_PowerPoint|PPT]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。
